{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "权力帮沙家四兄弟袭击萧家剑庐，被神秘老仆张妈（实为隐侠张临意）一剑击杀三人。张临意审问沙雷，得知权力帮由沙千灯、孔扬秦、华孤坟率领三百余人进犯，另有无名护法已到、一洞护法将至。老夫人收留沙雷。萧西楼以步法战胜孔扬秦，朱侠武以气势压倒沙千灯，沙千灯毁红灯逃遁。浣花剑派以蓄水克火击退权力帮全力进攻。张临意为康出渔疗毒，萧秋水在回廊遭神秘人偷袭，以口咬剑锋化解危机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_yun",
      "speaker_name": "沙云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“一刀断魂！”",
      "tone": "齐喊",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“老大、老四，你看老二……”",
      "tone": "骇然",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“张妈，饶他不杀吧。”",
      "tone": "慈祥庄严",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_furen",
      "text": "“萧夫人，为了老身，使你受伤，者身真无以为报……”",
      "tone": "歉疚",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_furen",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“晚辈等保护夫人不力，反幸张妈……张老前辈拔剑相助，晚辈实在愧煞……”",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“张妈，请这小友说几句话。”",
      "tone": "平和",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“你们一共来了几人？”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“三百……三百六十多人。”",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“是些什么人？”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“家师、孔护法、华护法各带了帮中一百名子弟，还有六十余人，是我们四兄弟、南宫世兄、以及孔护法三位弟子的友人。”",
      "tone": "如实",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“主帅就只是沙千灯、孔扬秦、华孤坟三人么？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "顺从",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“张临意……”",
      "tone": "痛呼",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“你说谎。”",
      "tone": "冷峻",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“没有人能对我说谎。”",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“我再问你一次，‘九天十地，十九人魔，来了几个？’”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“已来了四个……”",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“将来的呢？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“还有一个。”",
      "tone": "低头",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“是了。我道李沉舟要毁浣花派，掳老夫人，怎只会派三个来……另外两个是谁？”",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“我不知道。”",
      "tone": "惊恐",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“我……我真的不知道。我只知道已来的是‘无名护法’，快来的是‘一洞护法’，他们俩，我……我真的没有见过！”",
      "tone": "慌乱",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“来了的是谁？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_lei",
      "speaker_name": "沙雷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“无名护法。”",
      "tone": "顺从",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“你去吧。”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“要是你觉得无所适从，那就留在我身边吧。”",
      "tone": "慈祥",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“张妈，萧夫人受伤了，你替她治疗一下。”",
      "tone": "吩咐",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_furen",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“我不碍事。‘观鱼楼’中还有一位康先生，中了华孤坟的毒，还请张前辈劳顾一下。”",
      "tone": "客气",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好。”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“你去吧，敌人已退，你不用老照顾我。”",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_sha_lei",
      "text": "“你跟我来……”",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xiao_furen",
      "text": "“娘，老夫人到底是谁？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_furen",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“张前辈。‘观鱼楼’在回廊前方左侧，转弯就到……”",
      "tone": "指引",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xiao_furen",
      "text": "“妈！”",
      "tone": "惊叫",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我先救她，再去观鱼阁。你抬你母亲先进‘振眉阁’”",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你爹自会料理，要是浣花派连这也应付不过去，那也命中该绝了，你快带我去‘观鱼阁’。”",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“张前辈，在下先领你去医疗康先生，至于浣花剑派的事，就算我派应付自如，但在下作为浣花弟子，当然要去共担，虽死不辞，哪有一个人独保平安的事！”",
      "tone": "慷慨",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“好。”",
      "tone": "赞许",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“近十年来，你是唯一敢与我顶撞的后辈。”",
      "tone": "赞许",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“五毒血汁。”",
      "tone": "惊呼",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "text": "“张前辈，您一定要设法救救我师父！”",
      "tone": "哀求",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他中的是华孤坟的毒？”",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“华百毒的毒又精深了。”",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "张临意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“只好先服这‘三生草还丹’试试，泡在酒里，烘热调好，才可以食用。”",
      "tone": "郑重",
      "chapter": 7
    }
  ],
